    <briefdescription>
<para>Direct deserialization target for the Taillard JSON benchmark format. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Field names match the JSON keys exactly to allow zero-configuration deserialization via <ref refid="namespace_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_unity" kindref="compound">Unity</ref>&apos;s <computeroutput>JsonUtility</computeroutput> or <computeroutput>System.Text.Json</computeroutput>. After deserialization, <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_data_1_1_taillard_instance_1af2bd50c21201cbe57bd256239db584d6" kindref="member">JobCount</ref> and <ref refid="class_assets_1_1_scripts_1_1_scheduling_1_1_data_1_1_taillard_instance_1a7207f47edf07e7ec6704d88cadebd4c4" kindref="member">MachineCount</ref> are derived from the matrix dimensions, and GetJobOperations provides the typed operation pairs consumed by DESSimulator.LoadInstance. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
